rt emts program throughout the period of performance vse will support the product manager pdm for the aav test vehicles located at our aav maintenance facility at green road ruther glen va and multiple conus and oconus locations maintaining and testing the pdm aav vehicles is the first step in moderizing the aav family of vehicles fov since the marine corps has extended the service life of the aav to  “for nearly two decades we have provided comprehensive maintenance support for the usmc amphibious assault vehicles” said federal services group president jr brown “our program manager maintenance supervisor and mechanics engineers vehicle operators and field service technicians bring expertise experience and a level of detailed knowledge that will continue to keep these vehicles in the highest state of operational readiness for testing and demonstrations throughout their service life our number one goal is to ensure that our nation’s first line of defense is fully supported to accomplish their mission” about vse established in  vse is a diversified logistics and services company with experience in solving issues of global significance with integrity agility and value vse is dedicated to making our federal and commercial clients successful by delivering innovative solutions for vehicle ship and aircraft sustainment supply chain management platform modernization mission enhancement program management energy it and consulting services for additional information regarding vse services and products please see the companys web site at wwwvsecorpcom or contact christine kaineg vse investor relations at   view source version on businesswirecom httpwwwbusinesswirecomnewshomeen vse news contactchristine kaineg  source vse corporation released september     us gao  vse corporation skip navigation advanced search reports  testimoniesbid protests appropriations lawkey issuesabout gaocareersmultimedia resources presidential and congressional transition for congress for journalists 